f="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-pushes-back-for-all-the-dogs-album-release-3498864">已从 9 月 22 日推迟到 10 月 6 日</a>。</p><p>这位艺术家透露，他面临着“两难”的境地：要么推迟现场表演以“完成专辑”，要么推迟专辑。</p><p> “好吧，我面临的困境是我要么取消演出来完成专辑，要么完成任务并在最后一场演出之前放弃专辑。</p><p> “我欠你们我们正在建立的所有这些记忆，无论我们迄今为止错过了什么，我们肯定都会倒回去。”</p><p>他接着说“这是正确的”，新专辑将于 10 月 6 日发行，以便他有时间完成演出和专辑。</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-enlists-sza-for-new-single-slime-you-3498888">Drake 招募 SZA 创作新单曲《Slime You》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
阿黛尔表示她在拉斯维加斯演出期间不再自拍https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-says-shes-no-longer-take-selfies-during-her-las-vegas-shows-3498880?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=adele-says-她在拉斯维加斯演出期间不再自拍Elizabeth AubreySat, 16 Sep 2023 10:54:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsCoronavirusPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3498880 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿黛尔在拉斯维加斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我正命悬一线，努力不感染新冠病毒”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-says-shes-no-longer-taking-selfies-during-her-las-vegas-shows-3498880">阿黛尔表示她在拉斯维加斯演出期间不再自拍的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿黛尔在拉斯维加斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adele-performing-at-her-Las-Vegas-residency-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>表示，她将无法再在拉斯维加斯演出期间与粉丝自拍。</p><p>这位音乐家的拉斯维加斯驻场演出将于 11 月结束，他表示，这一决定归咎于<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coronavirus">新冠</a>病例的增加。</p><p>在拉斯维加斯期间，阿黛尔经常拍摄视频并与观众中的粉丝合影。</p><p> “通常情况下，我绝对会停下来聊天，听听你的生活，成为一个爱管闲事的人，”阿黛尔在她最近的节目中说道。 “然而，我正坚持不懈地努力不感染新冠病毒”（来自<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/164541/Adele-no-longer-taking-selfies-during-Las-Vegas-shows" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐新闻</em></a>）。</p><p> “我认识的和我一起工作的每个人都他妈的感染了新冠病毒，所以我还没感染真是个奇迹，”她补充道。 “我真的很喜欢和你聊天，但我不想生病，我会远远地自拍或者拍你的视频。</p><p> “我可能会出现症状，然后我就无法参加我的演出，如果我再取消这些演出，那我就该死了。我拒绝取消任何演出。我只是不能冒生病的风险。老实说，我的免疫系统已经很差了，我想靠近你之类的，但我不能冒险。”</p><p>她继续说道：“最后一场演出两天后，我在最后一次休息时患了流感，我很兴奋……我不介意在休息时患上流感。我不介意在休息期间生病。我还有九个星期的时间。这是我的第 26 个周末。上周六这是我的第 50 场演出，感觉就像一个里程碑。”</p><p>在凯撒宫斗兽场举办的“与阿黛尔共度周末”驻场演出将于 11 月 4 日结束。 </p><figure id="attachment_3483822" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3483822" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3483822" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270.jpg" alt="阿黛尔在凯撒宫罗马斗兽场举行的“阿黛尔周末”驻场开幕式上登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adele@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3483822" class="wp-caption-text">阿黛尔在凯撒宫斗兽场举行的“阿黛尔周末”驻场开幕式上登台表演。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时，一位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-fan-who-she-defended-from-security-thanks-her-in-video-message-3489944">阿黛尔粉丝在最近的一场维加斯演出中受到阿黛尔保安的保护，他在 TikTok 上发布的一条消息中向她表示感谢。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-stops-vegas-show-to-defend-fan-from-security-guard-3489218">阿黛尔最近在发现歌迷被保安和其他音乐会观众告知后停止了一场演出</a>。</p><p> “自从我站起来以来，那个年轻的球迷就一直受到困扰，这是怎么回事？他怎么了？她说。</p><p>在确认了这名粉丝的身份后，她对保安说：“你们为什么要打扰他？你可以让他一个人静一静吗？”</p><p>然后她对粉丝补充道：“他们不会再打扰你了，亲爱的。你很享受这个节目。”</p><p>这位粉丝自称是 TikTok 用户@juanp_lastra，并在标题中写道：“阿黛尔非常感谢你度过了这个激动人心的夜晚，感谢你为我挺身而出，这样我才能以应有的方式体验你的演唱会。我也很抱歉我没有回复你问我的任何问题。你开始跟我说话，我几乎停止了呼吸。</p><p> “我计划来参加这场音乐会已经一年多了，我终于有机会见到这个地球上最美丽、最光荣的女人。我仍然无法接受这样一个事实：我和阿黛尔在同一个房间，和她一起唱每一首歌，她甚至停止了演出来为我辩护。”</p><p> He added: “I did not expected everyone in my section to be mad at me for having the time of my life and wanting to stand up and sing with her but I honestly did not care at all about what anyone was saying to me I just was in awe with the master piece I was watching with my own eyes. I did not have time for them haters.”</p><p> Elsewhere in Adele&#39;s Vegas residency, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-helps-couple-with-gender-reveal-at-las-vegas-residency-watch-footage-3483817">the singer helped a couple reveal the gender of their baby</a> at one of the recent shows.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-says-shes-no-longer-taking-selfies-during-her-las-vegas-shows-3498880">Adele says she&#39;s no longer taking selfies during her Las Vegas shows</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
